== 評價 ==
任天堂在2010年底進行跨越前四代正式精靈寶可夢人氣投票，阿爾宙斯被評選為第一名，超越了達克萊伊、[[喵喵_(神奇寶貝)|喵喵]]和[[皮卡丘|皮卡丘]]等寶可夢<ref name="1up">{{cite web|title=Pokemon Black/White: How a Pokemon Comes to America|url=http://www.1up.com/previews/pokemon-blackwhite-coming-america?pager.offset=1|first=Kat|last=Bailey|publisher=1up Games|work=1up.com|date=2011-01-31|accessdate=2011-11-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120419002214/http://www.1up.com/previews/pokemon-blackwhite-coming-america?pager.offset=1|archivedate=2012-04-19}} </ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/21237/news/most-popular-pokemon-revealed/ |title=Nintendo News: Most popular Pokemon revealed |publisher=Official Nintendo Magazine |date=2010-11-08 |accessdate=2011-12-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110219224646/http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/21237/news/most-popular-pokemon-revealed/ |archivedate=2011-02-19 }} </ref>。任天堂官方雜誌的克里斯·斯庫利將阿爾宙斯排在10個最好的寶可夢之中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/16559/features/10-best-pokmon/ |title=Nintendo Feature: 10 Best Pokémon |publisher=Official Nintendo Magazine |date=2010-04-24 |accessdate=2011-12-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111016023734/http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/16559/features/10-best-pokmon/ |archivedate=2011-10-16 }} </ref>。

