的喬納森·福爾摩斯則是把阿爾宙斯評論為“將[[遊戲王|遊戲王]]的怪獸和[[魔法公主|魔法公主]]的山獸神的負面結合”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.destructoid.com/god-of-pokemon-dlc-coming-next-month-to-toys-r-us-152487.phtml |title=God of Pokemon DLC coming next month to Toys R Us |publisher=Destructoid |date= |accessdate=2011-12-07 |archive-date=2019-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912192544/https://www.destructoid.com/god-of-pokemon-dlc-coming-next-month-to-toys-r-us-152487.phtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，一位日本電影編輯寫道，阿爾宙斯在電影中未被充分利用，牠應該「可以被用來更好地傳達故事，牠是有如神一般的寶可夢」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://japancinema.net/2010/05/05/pokemon-arceus-and-the-jewel-of-life-review/ |title=Pokémon: Arceus and the Jewel of Life – Review |publisher=Japan Cinema |date=1988-10-31 |accessdate=2011-12-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111016015219/http://japancinema.net/2010/05/05/pokemon-arceus-and-the-jewel-of-life-review/ |archivedate=2011-10-16 }} </ref>。

